@cindex cache

@process{Cache} process manage the local server storage place. Files into cache's directories called @file{toKeep} will never be deleted. Symlink are not followed.

@process{Cache} use 3 options define into the 
@dataConf{} file:
@table @code
@item cacheSize
the maximum size that limit growing operations into the cache
@item cacheTTL
the minimum time a file notifyed to 
@actorUser{} has to be keept into the cache
@item queryTTL
the time to live of a @actorUserO{} query is keept into the
@dataChecksum{} file
@end table

